      "text": "Un Elixus fazzija us to:\nRo buhs man tew darriht? stah-\nsti man/ kas irr tawá Namuná?\nUn winna fazzija : Tawai Kal-\nponei irr wiﬀai neneeka Nam-\nmâ/ ka titcai weena Etjes-\nKruhse.\n"
