      "text": "Tad fazzija wiꞥſch : Eij/\npraﬃ Traukus preeſſch tewis\nno ahrenes/ no wiﬀeem taveem\nRaimineem luhdst tukſchus Trau-\nkus ne masu Pulku.\n"
