      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nahz eekſcha/ un ais-\nflehdsf Durwis pakkat tewis/ un\npakkat taweem Dehleem/ pehz\neeleij eekſch wiﬀeem Traukeem/\nnn pildijnji leez tohs pee Mallas.\n"
