      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nogahje ta no winna/\nnn aisflehdsf tahs Durwis pak-\nkat fewis/ un pakkat faweem\nDehleem/ tee atneffe winnai tohs\nTraukus/ un winna eelehje.\n"
