    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad tee Trauki villi\nbija/ tad fazzija ta us sawu Deh-\nlu: Neſs man wehl weenu Trau-\nku. Bet tas fazzija us to: Ne-\nwaſd wairs Trauku: Tad stah-\nweja ta Efje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta nahze/ undewe tam\nDeeva Wihrain Sixnu : Un\nwiꞥſch fazzija : Eij/ pahrdohd to\nEfji/ un makfa tawani Parradu-\nDsinnejam. Uu no ta zitta us-\nturrajs patti at taweem Dehleem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tas notiffahs tahdá Lai-\nkâ/ kad Elixus zaur Sunemi\ngahje/ tad tur bija weena bagga-\nta Seewa/ ta usluhdse winnu/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ka tas Maiſi ehſtu. Kad nn\nwiꞥſch daschkahrt zaurgahje/ tad\ngahje wiꞥſch tur eekſcha/ un eh-\nde pee tahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta fazzija ustawu Wiḫ-\nru: Redsjelle/ es nomainnu/ ka\nſchts Deetwa Wihrs twehts irr/\nkas weenumebr ſche pahrstaiga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Darrifim jelle winnam-\nweenu masu Raimbariti no Gal-\ndeem/ un likſim winnam tur\nweenu Guttu/ un weenu Galdu/\nun Krebslu/un Lufturi/ ka wiꞥſch\npee mums nahkdains tur warb\nee-eet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas gaddijahs weena\nDeená/ kad wiꞥſch tur nahze/\ntad gahje wiꞥſch tai augſta Raim-\nbariti/ un apgullehs tur.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija us Ge-\nasu fawu Puiki : Aizina ſcho\nSunamitereni. Un wiꞥſch aizi-\nnaja to/ un ta nahze preeſſch\nwinna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija us to:\nSakki jelle winnai! Redſi/ tu\neſſi ar wiﬀu ſcho Gahdafhanu\npar mums gadajji/ ko buhs\nman tew darriht? Irng tewis\ndeht kas jarunna pee ta Kelni-\nna/ jeb pee to Karra Leel-Kungu?\nbet winna fazzija: Es dsihwoju\nwiddu starp manneem Laudim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiꞥſch: Ko\ntad es tew zittadi darrischu? Un\nGeasus fazzija: Winnai Dehla\nnewaid/ un winnas Wihrs irr\nwezz.\n"
    },
